{"tid":1671791,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【又走一個】大隻仔溫家偉離開TVB 轉戰新加坡","createTime":"2019-10-23T16:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T01:28:45.000Z","uid":44730,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"d992a6846922ff3bdd468a61e66eb2f82b46794f","tid":1671791,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T16:49:53.000Z","msg":"近月有不少人藝人相繼離開或不獲續約，08年參加港男，現年32歲的「大隻仔」溫家偉亦在IG表示與無綫結束10年賓主關係，轉到新加坡發展。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/10/1571837280_at-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F10%2F1571837280_at-1280w.png&h=6ae1e614&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3a5eff720e770d2f3edfbd7da36a245467376b5","tid":1671791,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T16:50:17.000Z","msg":"日前在IG寫道︰「It&rsquo;s official!!! My contract with TVB has ended!!!!&nbsp;首先我想多謝TVB畀咁多機會喺呢10年。如果冇TVB就冇呢一個大隻仔。其實10年過得好快。我仲記得我第一次行入TVB，一個好驚，唔識講中文嘅小朋友。不過因為佢哋，我學識咗好多嘢。我想喺呢度多謝所有監製、導演，同埋任何人幫到我，畀個機會我。希望有一日我哋可以再見面。我會繼續努力喺香港發展。」"},{"pid":"a2fcef85a1c7db12472a52218a5ff7624c412e6c","tid":1671791,"uid":44730,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T16:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/10/1571837285_eK-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F10%2F1571837285_eK-1280w.png&h=e9719fb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16fd1c45180866e591074c53ec50ffb7b6ccefa6","tid":1671791,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T16:50:59.000Z","msg":"溫家偉在TVB的發展平平，參與的劇集角色大多是閒角，最多戲份的要數到《特技人》扮演的「芝麻」，而最為人熟悉的是他主持的《搵食飯團》。至於離巢原因，他坦言想拍劇，但TVB手上工作以飲食節目、綜藝節目為主，大家理念有偏差，洽談了一段時間最後都拉倒了。近年他在新加坡的發展不俗，他在新加坡擔正的劇集《Last Madame》更打破了當地首播收視紀錄！大隻仔有條件向外闖不無道理，他表示在在當地發展順利，還望物色經理人繼續在中、港兩地發展。"},{"pid":"657b772b3ec36777288b846ec725d3a529932093","tid":1671791,"uid":132544,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T16:52:07.000Z","msg":"就變亞視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw who?.gif"},{"pid":"44f0b919203d43a9b3d1a5b19a42f4bb829f151d","tid":1671791,"uid":288648,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T16:54:06.000Z","msg":"其實佢幾靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早走早着 祝你發展得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d011e1d7b1c926aea54d0a72f52c41c0a9fdec","tid":1671791,"uid":44730,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T16:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/10/1571837276_LQ-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F10%2F1571837276_LQ-1280w.jpg&h=7b3ba74d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似幾型？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9bc93f1c3ca2ed0d3770116690261e511a77e9a3","tid":1671791,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T16:59:55.000Z","msg":"做開奸角<br />\n法國混血？"},{"pid":"f1e85a8f7ef9ea7e05d62440113c70c72c12e21a","tid":1671791,"uid":3189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T17:29:17.000Z","msg":"又靚仔又大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點會冇出路"},{"pid":"d6d2291d16b3babdd2e823972fbfa230f5caf3d3","tid":1671791,"uid":550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T17:52:29.000Z","msg":"淨係記得佢喺明珠台報過天氣"},{"pid":"af731d6aeea4b19e58077b8d2d7f94a77011b74c","tid":1671791,"uid":195904,"like":1